"\nSTAVES"
"\n"
"\nThe rare Yokudan war-wizards employed staves designed to resemble melee weapons to borrow some of the prestige of hand-to-hand combat. Their metallic finials might be round, flared, or pointed in the ""broad arrowhead"" design."
