"\n"
"\nSWORDS"
"\n"
"\nDwarven swords look like mere extensions of their daggers, featuring the same broad, triangular blades with both point and edge. Their cross-guards are slender to almost nonexistent, which argues that Dwemer swordplay did not rely much on thrusting."
msgstr "レイノー・ヴァノス著\\r"
